trans-unit.source: Passed to custom WSDL exporters and importers to enable customization of the metadata export and import processes for a WSDL endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Passata a utilità di esportazione WSDL personalizzata e importazione per abilitare la personalizzazione dell'esportazione dei metadati e importare i processi per un endpoint WSDL.

trans-unit.source: The WsdlEndpointConversionContext class represents the context in which the custom WSDL for an endpoint is either exported using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> or imported using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: La classe WsdlEndpointConversionContext rappresenta il contesto in cui le informazioni WSDL personalizzate per un endpoint è che uno esportato utilizzando <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>o importati utilizzando <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The following properties enable you to retrieve the WSDL document object model for the current WSDL: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A> property gets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName> for the endpoint contract.
trans-unit.target: Le proprietà seguenti consentono di recuperare il modello a oggetti documento WSDL per il WSDL corrente: - il <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A>proprietà ottiene il <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName>per il contratto dell'endpoint.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A> property gets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName> for the current endpoint.
- The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A> property gets the binding for the current endpoint.
- The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A> property gets the port for the current endpoint.

- - The following methods enable you to add or remove custom WSDL elements to the appropriate scopes in the exported or imported WSDL: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A> method returns the fault binding for the specified fault.
trans-unit.target: -I metodi seguenti consentono di aggiungere o rimuovere elementi WSDL personalizzati dagli ambiti appropriati nel WSDL esportato o importato: - il <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A>metodo restituisce l'associazione di errore per l'errore specificato.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A> method returns the fault for the specified fault binding.
trans-unit.target: -La <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A>metodo restituisce l'errore per l'associazione di errore specificato.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A> method returns the message binding for the specified message.
trans-unit.target: -La <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A>metodo restituisce l'associazione di messaggio per il messaggio specificato.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A> method returns the message for the specified message binding.
trans-unit.target: -La <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A>metodo restituisce il messaggio per l'associazione di un messaggio specificato.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A> method returns the operation binding for the specified operation.
trans-unit.target: -La <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A>metodo restituisce l'associazione di operazione per l'operazione specificata.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A> method returns the operation for the specified operation binding.
trans-unit.target: -La <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A>metodo restituisce l'operazione per l'associazione di operazione specificato.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A>
